night talking about your ex-boyfriend.

237
00:13:04,920 --> 00:13:07,229
-l'm such an idiot.
-No, you're not.

238
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:08,914
Well, maybe not an idiot.

239
00:13:09,160 --> 00:13:12,277
But certainly not as smart as...
Someone we won't mention.

240
00:13:13,199 --> 00:13:14,154
Thank you.

241
00:13:14,519 --> 00:13:17,716
