I'm free on Thursday.

242
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:20,595
-Hey, they're leaving.
-What? Here, gimme, gimme.

243
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:25,114
Oh, my God, oh, my God.
They're coming right towards us.

244
00:13:25,360 --> 00:13:27,476
