248
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:35,995
Oh, no!

249
00:13:40,160 --> 00:13:41,434
She just hit my car!

250
00:13:42,519 --> 00:13:44,111
What are you guys doing here?

251
00:13:44,599 --> 00:13:47,272
Hi, Ames! What're you doing here?

252
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:52,158
-What happened?
-OMG.

253
00:13:52,800 --> 00:13:55,268
-Aren't you Leonard Hofstadter?
-Yeah?

254
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:57,835
I saw you speak at Stanford
with Sheldon Cooper.

255
00:13:58,159 --> 00:14:01,390
Amy, can you believe it?
It's Dr. Leonard Hofstadter!

256
00:14:02,520 --> 00:14:04,033
No, pinch me!

257
00:14:04,759 --> 00:14:06,989
It's an absolute pleasure to meet you.
Can I shake your hand?

258
00:14:07,680 --> 00:14:10,353
I don't know if you want to do that,
lwasjust... Okay, never mind.

259
00:14:11,800 --> 00:14:14,678
-Amy, I'm never washing this hand again.
-You really should.

260
00:14:17,879 --> 00:14:20,791
60 seconds, this is not looking good.

261
00:14:21,079 --> 00:14:22,717
One minute is a long time.

262
00:14:23,160 --> 00:14:25,151
Oh, I've been telling women that
for 20 years.

263
00:14:28,360 --> 00:14:30,794
-45.
-45 seconds is plenty of time

264
00:14:30,999 --> 00:14:34,071
for a woman to walk through that door
and fall in love with me.

265
00:14:34,439 --> 00:14:37,078
And probably half that
if I break out the old cow eyes.

266
00:14:38,399 --> 00:14:39,468
30 seconds.

267
00:14:39,920 --> 00:14:40,875
Uh-oh.

268
00:14:41,199 --> 00:14:44,350
-What if it's Jennifer Lawrence?
-What?

269
00:14:44,759 --> 00:14:46,954
Oh, that last Hunger Games
was not my cup of tea.

270
00:14:47,719 --> 00:14:49,550
