at the last possible moment.

274
00:14:58,639 --> 00:15:02,314
Ugh. Sounds like a drama queen. Oh, no.
It is Jennifer Lawrence.

275
00:15:04,319 --> 00:15:10,428
Five, four, three, two, one.

276
00:15:15,520 --> 00:15:16,873
That's too bad.

277
00:15:17,199 --> 00:15:19,190
Maybe we did make the test too difficult.

278
00:15:19,480 --> 00:15:21,550
(SIGHS) I don't think it matters.
Look, Sheldon,

279
00:15:21,759 --> 00:15:23,795
I believe when the time is right
for you to meet someone,

280
00:15:24,159 --> 00:15:25,558
it'll just happen, okay?

281
00:15:25,759 --> 00:15:27,715
Not because of a test or a website,
but because--

282
00:15:27,920 --> 00:15:28,875
