and she's really pretty!

285
00:15:41,240 --> 00:15:42,195
Answer it!

286
00:15:42,999 --> 00:15:44,273
All right.

287
00:15:50,080 --> 00:15:51,195
Can I help you?

288
00:15:51,719 --> 00:15:54,313
Um, are you the physicist
that placed the ad on Craigslist?

289
00:15:54,800 --> 00:15:57,439
-Yes.
-Hi, I'm Vanessa Bennett.

290
00:15:57,800 --> 00:16:00,439
Sorry it took a while for me to get here.
I was stuck in this boring symposium

291
00:16:00,639 --> 00:16:03,233
on atomic spectroscopy
when I came across your ad.

292
00:16:03,479 --> 00:16:04,594
And it saved my night. (CHUCKLES)

293
00:16:04,800 --> 00:16:06,358
The puzzles were really fun.

294
00:16:06,599 --> 00:16:10,672
I've never had to translate Klingon
into ancient Sanskrit before.

295
00:16:13,280 --> 00:16:15,157
Careful, it's addictive.

296
00:16:17,280 --> 00:16:19,157
(SPEAKING OTHER LANGUAGE)

297
00:16:22,399 --> 00:16:24,037
Or as they say in Sanskrit,

298
00:16:25,240 --> 00:16:27,834
