299
00:16:28,999 --> 00:16:31,274
And just like that,
you're a Klingon-Sanskrit junkie.

300
00:16:32,680 --> 00:16:34,989
Anyway, ljust knew
I had to meet the person responsible

301
00:16:35,359 --> 00:16:36,758
for such a brilliant idea.

302
00:16:37,039 --> 00:16:39,314
And I don't need to tell you there aren't
a lot of men who love physics,

303
00:16:39,519 --> 00:16:42,238
archaic languages and flags of the world.

304
00:16:43,400 --> 00:16:45,277
I am a bit of a unicorn.

305
00:16:46,560 --> 00:16:48,949
Well, you certainly seem
like a special lady,

306
00:16:49,160 --> 00:16:50,832
uh, but as you know,
you missed the deadline,

307
00:16:51,039 --> 00:16:52,028
so thanks for playing.

308
00:16:55,120 --> 00:16:56,075
What?

309
00:16:59,759 --> 00:17:01,272
How could you send her away?

310
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:03,272
She was late.

311
00:17:04,439 --> 00:17:08,717
