-No problem.

314
00:17:19,519 --> 00:17:22,352
-l'm really sorry about your car.
-Oh, it's all right.

315
00:17:22,600 --> 00:17:24,750
If you're free next weekend,
I'd love to take you out again.

316
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:26,355
Um...

317
00:17:26,599 --> 00:17:30,478
Listen, you're a really nice guy,
but I don't think this is working out.

318
00:17:31,639 --> 00:17:32,867
Oh. Okay.

319
00:17:33,199 --> 00:17:35,076
Um... I'm really sorry.

320
00:17:35,359 --> 00:17:36,269
Oh...

321
00:17:36,680 --> 00:17:39,990
At least the same woman
that rejected Sheldon Cooper rejected me.

322
00:17:42,439 --> 00:17:43,792
There ya go. (CHUCKLES)

323
00:17:44,999 --> 00:17:47,035
If I ever do meet him,
we'll have that in common.

324
00:17:47,559 --> 00:17:49,231
Sure. (CHUCKLES)

325
00:17:49,520 --> 00:17:52,956
And he's kissed you and I've kissed you,
so if you think about it--

